      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZABDON IS BACK (6) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing eighth (26.40) at this track in a Grade 5. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. KOOLBOO KID (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 2 lengths away in third (24.06) behind Mr. Williams at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Will give a great sight again. SEEK TO FLY (2) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 5th (24.46) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Should be about the money. DOZEN DONUTS (8) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
